title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 2 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 2 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Clay and Buck talk EIB 24/7. Cuomo tells businesses: Go to vaccine-only admission. Nobody knows what's in the infrastructure bill. Eviction moratorium ends, Democrats want to extend it, closest they've ever come to universal basic income. Elizabeth Warren: Eviction moratorium improves health.
